Bot-BasicBot-Pluggable-TranslateBot

A translation bot module for Perl Bot::BasicBot?::Pluggable bots.

Provides commands to translate text to and from various languages, and supports
automatic translation, whereby you can request that the bot translate everything
you say until you ask it to stop. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Bot::BasicBot::Pluggable::TranslateBot

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Bot-BasicBot-Pluggable-TranslateBot

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Bot-BasicBot-Pluggable-TranslateBot

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Bot-BasicBot-Pluggable-TranslateBot

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Bot-BasicBot-Pluggable-TranslateBot/


